room_title: Escape room "The Hall of Zombie" by House of Clues in Houston
room_address: 3500 West Davis St., Suite 300 Conroe, TX 77304
room_description: It's pitch black. Lights only flicker occasionally. Maybe you took a wrong turn somewhere. But when you try to leave, the door is locked. And then you hear it. There is someone in here with you, and you better find you way out of here, and fast.
